{"title":"C1 Introduction&Convex Hulls","uid":"df5af6f71edb87ae26fa2c44cce1ef6b","slug":"ComputionalGeometry/C0 绪论","date":"2021-10-01T09:14:33.000Z","updated":"2021-10-01T09:15:10.153Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ComputionalGeometry/C0 绪论.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Introduction\"><a href=\"#Introduction\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Introduction\"></a>Introduction</h1><h2 id=\"Foreword\"><a href=\"#Foreword\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Foreword\"></a>Foreword</h2><h3 id=\"Homework\"><a href=\"#Homework\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Homework\"></a>Homework</h3><ul>\n<li>顶会外文文献选一篇文章，一周内，抓阄确定报告顺序<ul>\n<li>主题<ul>\n<li>图形、图像、机器人、计算几何、涉及到与图形相关的皆可</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>建议<ul>\n<li>教材上面的关键词</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>CGAL开源工具下载安装，讲过的算法可以直接嵌入<ul>\n<li>不要看代码先自己实现</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>写读书报告<ul>\n<li>课程教学了什么</li>\n<li>小论文报告体会</li>\n<li>CGAL应用的如何</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"About-Teacher\"><a href=\"#About-Teacher\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"About Teacher\"></a>About Teacher</h3><p>13487316328</p>\n<p>ysxiong@nudt.edu.cn</p>\n<h3 id=\"CG-vs-CV\"><a href=\"#CG-vs-CV\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CG vs CV\"></a>CG vs CV</h3><div class=\"table-container\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Input</th>\n<th>Output</th>\n<th>侧重</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>CG</td>\n<td>对虚拟场景的描述<br />通常为多边形数组<br />而每个多边形由三个顶点组成，每个顶点包括三维坐标、贴图坐标、rgb 颜色等</td>\n<td>图像<br />即二维像素数组</td>\n<td>拓扑结构</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CV</td>\n<td>图像或图像序列<br />通常来自相机、摄像头或视频文件</td>\n<td>对于图像序列对应的真实世界的理解<br />比如检测人脸、识别车牌</td>\n<td>信息提取</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DIP</td>\n<td>图像</td>\n<td>图像<br />模糊、灰度化、增强对比度等</td>\n<td>图像本身信息变换</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/dd44910dd5928eea0206c2c1c200458d_r.jpg\" alt=\"preview\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/20672053/answer/15854031\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/20672053/answer/15854031</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/20672053/answer/49951399\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/20672053/answer/49951399</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/hanlin_tan/article/details/50447895\">https://blog.csdn.net/hanlin_tan/article/details/50447895</a></p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"What’s-Computional-Geometry？\"><a href=\"#What’s-Computional-Geometry？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"What’s Computional Geometry？\"></a>What’s Computional Geometry？</h3><p>计算几何：几何图形的几何算法设计</p>\n<h3 id=\"Why？\"><a href=\"#Why？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Why？\"></a>Why？</h3><p>从底层开始$\\to$解决卡脖子问题</p>\n<h3 id=\"Some-Examples\"><a href=\"#Some-Examples\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Some Examples\"></a>Some Examples</h3><ul>\n<li>Look up the nearest public phone<ul>\n<li><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001112549157.png\" alt=\"image-20211001112549157\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /></li>\n<li>划分片区……$\\to$Voronoi diagram</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Short connection<ul>\n<li><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001112609272.png\" alt=\"image-20211001112609272\"></li>\n<li>机器人行走避障$\\to$P2P之间有没有一条连通的路</li>\n<li>Motion Planning of robotics</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>overlaying maps<ul>\n<li>结合两幅地图的信息</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Various-application-Domains\"><a href=\"#Various-application-Domains\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Various application Domains\"></a>Various application Domains</h3><ul>\n<li>Robotics</li>\n<li>CG</li>\n<li>CAD/CAM</li>\n<li>GIS</li>\n<li>Internet</li>\n<li>VR</li>\n<li>Virtual Surgery</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"Convex-Hulls\"><a href=\"#Convex-Hulls\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Convex Hulls\"></a>Convex Hulls</h2><h3 id=\"Good-Solutions\"><a href=\"#Good-Solutions\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Good Solutions\"></a>Good Solutions</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Good Solutions to algorithmic problems of a geometric nature based on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Thorough understanding of the <strong>geometric properties</strong> of the problems</li>\n<li>A proper application of <strong>algorithmic techniques</strong> and <strong>data structures</strong></li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Question-Description\"><a href=\"#Question-Description\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Question Description\"></a>Question Description</h3><p>A subset $S$ of the plane is called convex if and only if for any pair of points $p, q \\in S$ the line segment $\\overline{p q}$ is completely contained in $S$. The convex hull $\\mathrm{C} \\mathcal{H}(S)$ of a set $S$ is the smallest convex set that contains $S$. To be more precise, it is the intersection of all convex sets that contain $S$</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001112743799.png\" alt=\"image-20211001112743799\"></p>\n<p>即：</p>\n<p>给定一个平面点集，求取能够包含该平面点集中所有的点且为”凸”的顶点的顺序排列</p>\n<ul>\n<li>输入：点集</li>\n<li>输出：构成凸多边形的有序顶点</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001113005075.png\" alt=\"image-20211001113005075\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Algorithm-0：Divide-amp-Conquer\"><a href=\"#Algorithm-0：Divide-amp-Conquer\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Algorithm 0：Divide&amp;Conquer\"></a>Algorithm 0：Divide&amp;Conquer</h3><ul>\n<li>上包下包</li>\n<li>递归算法$\\to$递归出口问题</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Algorithm-1：SlowConvexHull\"><a href=\"#Algorithm-1：SlowConvexHull\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Algorithm 1：SlowConvexHull\"></a>Algorithm 1：<code>SlowConvexHull</code></h3><p><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001130929929.png\" alt=\"image-20211001130929929\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"思路解析\"><a href=\"#思路解析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路解析\"></a>思路解析</h4><pre class=\"mermaid\">graph TD\n初始化点集集合为空集\n--> 选取一对点p和q\n--> 选取第三个点r\n--所有点r皆在pq直线的右侧或直线上-->  p和q属于目标点集 \n\n选取第三个点r--有任一点r在pq直线的左侧--> p和q不属于目标点集</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"注意点\"><a href=\"#注意点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意点\"></a>注意点</h4><ul>\n<li><p>技术细节</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>if r lies to the left of the directed line from p to q</code>的程序表示<ul>\n<li>行列式$\\le0$</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Step5 can be performed in <strong>constant time</strong></li>\n<li>涉及到floating point arithmetic$\\to$不准确性$\\to$数据输入时<strong>有理化</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>特点</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Slow</li>\n<li>not robust</li>\n<li><p>degenerate cases are awkward</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>蛮力算法：$O(n^3)$</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>问题出现在哪里</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>穷举，任意两点都要计算</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Algorithm-2：incremental-algorithm\"><a href=\"#Algorithm-2：incremental-algorithm\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Algorithm 2：incremental algorithm\"></a>Algorithm 2：<code>incremental algorithm</code></h3><p><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001130957861.png\" alt=\"image-20211001130957861\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"思路解析-1\"><a href=\"#思路解析-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路解析\"></a>思路解析</h4><pre class=\"mermaid\">graph TD\n点集中所有点按照x轴坐标升序排列为点序列\n--> 将p_1和p_2加入到目标点集中\n--> 依次加入后面的点\n--make_a_right_turn--> 将该点加入到目标点集中\n\n--> 下半部分\n\n依次加入后面的点\n--do_not_make_a_right_turn--> 删除掉最后三个点中中间那个点\n\n--> 下半部分\n--> 删除上下重复的两个点</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"注意点-1\"><a href=\"#注意点-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意点\"></a>注意点</h4><ul>\n<li>技术细节<ul>\n<li><strong>有可能出现在凸包上的点</strong>上才进行<ul>\n<li>$[xmin,xmax,ymin,ymax]$</li>\n<li>对所有点按照x坐标进行排序</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>incremental</code>的来源<ul>\n<li>按照x坐标进行<strong>向前增量</strong>，构成<strong>左拐</strong>的点剔除掉</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>delete the middle</code><ul>\n<li><code>p_i</code>在当前看肯定在凸包上，要回看last three points</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>主要开销<ul>\n<li><strong>排序</strong><ul>\n<li>最坏$O(n^2)$</li>\n<li>最好$O(n)$</li>\n<li>最坏情况下的最好时间开销$O(nlogn)$</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>特点<ul>\n<li>use <strong>the lexicographic order</strong></li>\n<li>Left/right turn</li>\n<li><strong>floating point arithmetric</strong>$\\to$Compute a <strong>closed polygonnal chain</strong>$\\to$有理运算来避免浮点运算的误差</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"时间复杂度的证明\"><a href=\"#时间复杂度的证明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"时间复杂度的证明\"></a>时间复杂度的证明</h4><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>Theorem 1.1</strong></p>\n<p>The convex hull of a set of n points in the plane can be computed in $O(nlogn)$ time</p>\n<p><strong>Proof：</strong></p>\n<p>归纳法</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://rambo-1305767169.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/markdown/image-20211001133318321.png\" alt=\"image-20211001133318321\"></p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Degeneracies-and-robustness\"><a href=\"#Degeneracies-and-robustness\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Degeneracies and robustness\"></a>Degeneracies and robustness</h3><pre class=\"mermaid\">graph LR\nignore_everything\n--> degenerate_cases\n--> actual_implementation\n\n粗-->细-->robust</pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"课程补充资料\"><a href=\"#课程补充资料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"课程补充资料\"></